# Pin frontend assets against CDN tampering.
#
# Format: one "<sha256>  <path>" line per file (path relative to /app/static),
# matching the output of `sha256sum`. Lines starting with "#" are ignored
# (sha256sum -c skips them).
#
# To regenerate: clear this file (keeping the header), run `docker build .`,
# and copy the lines printed under "=== Vendor asset SHA-256 (audit me) ===".

